We use modules to stash away functionality

Some "interfaces"
- User
  * name, following, followers, keys, repositories
  + authenticate(username, password, options = {})
- Repository
  * vcs, name, owner, readers, writers, origin
  + create_repository(name, vcs)
  + remove_repository(name)
  + import(remote, type)
  + pull
  + log
- Key
  * key, name
  + add(user)
  + remove

